remixlab.bias.branch

Class MotionBranch<E extends Enum<E>,A extends Action<E>,C extends Action<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • remixlab.bias.branch.Branch<E>
      • remixlab.bias.branch.MotionBranch<E,A,C>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Reference action enum.
    A - Motion action enum sub-group.
    C - Click/tap action enum sub-group.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Copyable

    public class MotionBranch<E extends Enum<E>,A extends Action<E>,C extends Action<E>>
extends Branch<E>
    A Branch with a motionProfile(), defining some MotionShortcut / (motion) action mappings; and a clickProfile(), defining some ClickShortcut / (click) action mappings. Motion branches may be appended only to an GenericMotionAgent. See GenericMotionAgent.appendBranch(String).

    Note that all the methods provided here are simply wrappers to the motionProfile() and clickProfile(). See Profile.
